OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FWe can also report that mistakes in
OL,8,Fthe Single Justice Procedure (SJP)
OL,9,Fmeant at least one person was
OL,10,Fconvicted this year who was already
OL,11,Fdead.
OL,13,FIn response, the former lord chief
OL,14,Fjustice, who oversaw the introduction
OL,15,Fof the system, is now calling for the
OL,16,FMinistry of Justice (MoJ) to deliver
OL,17,Furgent reforms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/26
