OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FThe SJP was brought in in 2015 to
OL,8,Fspeed up magistrate court decisions,
OL,9,Fand it is now used for around 40,000
OL,10,Fcases every month in England and Wales.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe SJP, as it is commonly known, is
OL,18,Fdesigned to deal with what are
OL,19,Fperceived to be lower-level crimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/26
