OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FJust last month, the same system was
OL,8,Funder scrutiny when 74,000 people were
OL,9,Ftold their prosecutions for alleged
OL,10,Frail fare evasion could be overturned.
OL,12,FNow, our joint investigation has
OL,13,Funcovered a significant number of
OL,14,F"micro miscarriages of justice" -
OL,15,Fmainly in Driver and Vehicle Licensing
OL,16,FAgency (DVLA) and TV Licensing
OL,17,Foffences - where people are being
OL,18,Fconvicted because the prosecuting
OL,19,Fauthorities are not even reading their
OL,20,Fexplanations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/26
