OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FWe selected a sample size of 50 cases
OL,8,Fwhere defendants with strong
OL,9,Fextenuating circumstances had still
OL,10,Fbeen convicted under the SJP.
OL,12,FWe then asked a panel of four criminal
OL,13,Fbarristers to independently review the
OL,14,Fcases.
OL,16,FThey found almost three-quarters (74%)
OL,17,Fwere not in the public interest to
OL,18,Fprosecute in the first place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/26
