OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FJust a few days before Christmas last
OL,8,Fyear, Jenny had to take her three-
OL,9,Fmonth-old baby daughter into hospital
OL,10,Fdue to feeding problems.
OL,12,FBut baby Scarlett's condition worsened
OL,13,Fsuddenly, and she passed away
OL,14,Funexpectedly.
OL,16,FIt was during this period - in the
OL,17,Fdays between seeing her baby die, and
OL,18,Fthen the funeral - Jenny's car
OL,19,Finsurance lapsed for a single day
OL,20,Fbefore she remembered to renew it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/26
