OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FJenny was still grieving her baby's
OL,8,Fdeath when she received a letter from
OL,9,Fthe court telling her she was being
OL,10,Fprosecuted under the SJP.
OL,12,FIn a court, Jenny could have been
OL,13,Fgiven legal advice to plead not guilty
OL,14,Fdue to her circumstances, and she'd be
OL,15,Fgiven the chance to explain what
OL,16,Fhappened - but that is not the case in
OL,17,Fthis procedure done entirely on paper.
OL,19,F"I felt completely sign-posted to
OL,20,Fplead guilty," Jenny said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
