OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,F"I put in the 'mitigating
OL,8,Fcircumstances' that I didn't have
OL,9,Finsurance for the one day. So I
OL,10,Fthought, I have to plead guilty, then
OL,11,FI'll just explain what happened and
OL,12,Fthey'll understand."
OL,14,FHowever, Jenny was still convicted.
OL,16,F"They've overlooked my child's death,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/26
