OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,F"You find that magistrates are taking
OL,8,Fless and less time over the decisions
OL,9,Fthey're taking," he said.
OL,11,F"Some cases are being dealt with in 45
OL,12,Fseconds.
OL,14,F"It really confirms the suspicion that
OL,15,Fpeople have had all along that this is
OL,16,Fa conveyor belt of justice, rubber
OL,17,Fstamping people's convictions and
OL,18,Ffines, without giving them the
OL,19,Findividual consideration that they
OL,20,Freally deserve."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/26
