OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FLord Thomas was head of the courts in
OL,8,FEngland and Wales when the SJP was
OL,9,Ffirst introduced.
OL,11,FWe showed him our analysis, and the
OL,12,Fformer lord chief justice said it
OL,13,Fraises concerns about the SJP
OL,14,Fcontinuing in its current form.
OL,16,F"I think it's clear from what I've
OL,17,Fseen and from what the Magistrates'
OL,18,FAssociation are saying that there are
OL,19,Faspects of this procedure - very
OL,20,Fimportant aspects - that need
OL,21,Freviewing," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/26
