OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FLord Thomas added he was
OL,8,F"disappointed" to see that the SJP had
OL,9,Fnot been reformed before now.
OL,11,F"Fixing this is not difficult," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"It really is something the Ministry
OL,15,F(of Justice) and the prosecuting
OL,16,Fauthorities ought to consider with a
OL,17,Fdegree of urgency."
