OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FIn this case, the DVLA or the BBC for
OL,8,FTV Licensing offences conduct their
OL,9,Fown prosecutions through the SJP.
OL,11,FAt least one senior source in the DVLA
OL,12,Fsaid, off the record, they would
OL,13,Flikely have dropped many cases if they
OL,14,Fwere aware of the "mitigating
OL,15,Fcircumstances".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/26
