OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FThe DVLA formally responded to our
OL,8,Finvestigation with a statement,
OL,9,Fsaying: "A Single Justice Procedure
OL,10,Fnotice will only be issued when we
OL,11,Fhave exhausted all other enforcement
OL,12,Froutes, including issuing multiple
OL,13,Fitems of correspondence, to which the
OL,14,Fcustomer can respond to DVLA with
OL,15,Ftheir mitigation.
