OL,7,F"We give customers a number of
OL,8,Fopportunities to tell us about
OL,9,Fpersonal circumstances which may
OL,10,Fsignificantly affect their ability to
OL,11,Fstay licensed before and during the
OL,12,Fprosecution process, and we would
OL,13,Fencourage people to engage with us as
OL,14,Fearly as possible so we can properly
