OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FThe MoJ did not agree to an interview
OL,8,Fbut in a statement told us: "The
OL,9,FSingle Justice Procedure was designed
OL,10,Fto allow low-level offences to be
OL,11,Fdealt with simply and without people
OL,12,Fhaving to go to court unless they
OL,13,Fchoose to do so.
OL,15,F"The decision to prosecute cases under
OL,16,Fthe Single Justice Procedure is made
OL,17,Fby the prosecuting authority. This
OL,18,FGovernment is reviewing what more can
OL,19,Fbe done to support vulnerable
OL,20,Fdefendants, as well as how to improve
OL,21,Foversight and regulation."
