OL,3,C'They've overlooked my child's death':
OL,4,CWrongful prosecutions in legal
OL,5,Cprocedure
OL,7,FWhen asked if they had concerns about
OL,8,Fa dead person being prosecuted under
OL,9,Fthe Single Justice Procedure, they
OL,10,Ftold us a court cannot knowingly
OL,11,Fconvict someone who has died. And when
OL,12,Fsomeone who has died has been
OL,13,Fprosecuted, that prosecution will be
OL,14,Fvoid.
OL,16,FOur investigation has uncovered
OL,17,Fevidence of a system convicting people
OL,18,Fwho should not have been prosecuted.
