OL,7,FSome have been fined, some will pay
OL,8,Fmore for insurance for the rest of
OL,9,Ftheir lives because their explanations
OL,10,Fand pleas for compassion haven't even
OL,11,Fbeen read by those prosecuting them.
OL,13,FAnd despite the flaws we have exposed,
OL,14,Fthis system continues, unreformed, to
OL,15,Fconvict thousands in our courts every
OL,16,Fweek.
